<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1896-09-04T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1896-09-04T00:00:00-05:00" n="681" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d681">
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Taylor</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Olney</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Spain</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1896-09-04"><hi rend="italic">September 4,
                                    1896</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>Understood here <hi rend="italic">Competitor</hi> case already decided
                            annulling judgment and ordering new trial before ordinary tribunal.
                            Decision expected shortly.</p>
                    </div>
